name: GLAM BLACK SWAROVSKI CRYSTALS COCKTAIL RING
description:
GLAM BLACK SWAROVSKI CRYSTALS COCKTAIL RING

Absolutely gorgeous black deco style ring with swarovski crystals. 

Adjustable band to suit your finger and measures 1.8cm across.

High quality platinum alloy plating with intricate detail. Gorgeous ring embellished with clear Swarovski crystal detail on front. Wear this chic and stylish cocktail ring to update your look.

Looks great with any outfit! Glams it up! Sure to become your favourite glam ring!
